descriptionHtml: This mod adds two items that I felt should have been in the vanilla game to start with, the Potage le Magnifique and the Sunlight Souffle, from the book Uncommon Taste,I cant really test this mod because I am currently a belua sanguinare vampire and food has no effect on me, also I idealy want it so that these food options can only be made if you have read the cook book, but that exeeds my ability, so this mod is somewhat of a beta, enjoy, and don\'t forget the jarrin root :)
author: Ryuzaki1
